      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014not a single scratch or hiccup! It's been babied since day one and drives like it's brand new. You really have to see it to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
