    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, and the M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) executes lightning-fast gear swaps with crisp engagement. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; critical rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively with documented receipts. The chassis maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, free of subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system provides impeccable rebound and compression characteristics. The exterior retains its original finish with zero evidence of panel misalignment or paint correction, while the interior remains preserved with no bolster wear or UV degradation on the carbon leather trim. A turnkey collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak BMW M performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
