      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously preserved in showroom condition since the day it was delivered. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections to be found. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are free of even the slightest curb rash, wrapped in a matching set of premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and retains that fresh-from-the-factory scent; the leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at the dealership on a strict time-based schedule regardless of mileage. I have a comprehensive binder of every service receipt and inspection report since new. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road salt or inclement weather exposure. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
